item.description:
 &lt;p&gt;HadoopйғЁзҪІеҮҶеӨҮ жң¬ең°vmwareе®үиЈ… Linuxзі»з»ҹе®¶ж—Ҹдёӯ centos7 дёӢиҪҪең°еқҖ&lt;a href=&#34;http://101.110.118.58/isoredirect.centos.org/centos/7/isos/x86\_64/CentOS-7-x86\_64-Minimal-1611.iso&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener external nofollow noopener noreferrer&#34;&gt;http://101.110.118.58/isoredirect.centos.org/centos/7/isos/x86\_64/CentOS-7-x86\_64-Minimal-1611.iso&lt;/a&gt;   JavaеҜ№еә”зүҲжң¬1.8.0_121   HadoopзүҲжң¬2.8.0дёӢиҪҪең°еқҖ &lt;a href=&#34;http://mirror.bit.edu.cn/apache/hadoop/common/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener external nofollow noopener noreferrer&#34;&gt;http://mirror.bit.edu.cn/apache/hadoop/common/&lt;/a&gt; еҸҜд»Ҙж №жҚ®иҮӘе·ұе–ңеҘҪзҡ„зүҲжң¬дёӢиҪҪ&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;1-еҹәжң¬й…ҚзҪ®&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#1-еҹәжң¬й…ҚзҪ®&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;1.еҹәжң¬й…ҚзҪ®&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;1.еҹәжң¬й…ҚзҪ®&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;йҰ–е…Ҳе®үиЈ…дёҖдёӘcentos7е№¶й…ҚзҪ®еҘҪjava JavaзҺҜеўғй…ҚзҪ® жҲ‘зҡ„javaе®үиЈ…ең°еқҖ /usr/java/ jdk1.8.0_121   зј–иҫ‘javaзҺҜеўғ vi ~/.bash_profile ж·»еҠ жҲ–дҝ®ж”№ export JAVA_HOME=/usr/java/jdk1.8.0_121 export PATH=$JAVA_HOME/bin:$PATH жү§иЎҢ . ~/.bash_profile дҪҝеҸҳйҮҸз”ҹж•Ҳ  &lt;a id=&#34;more&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;2-sshй…ҚзҪ®&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#2-sshй…ҚзҪ®&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;2.sshй…ҚзҪ®&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;2.sshй…ҚзҪ®&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;е…Ҳ yum install ssh  е®үиЈ…   з„¶еҗҺжү§иЎҢ ssh-keygen -t dsa -P вҖҳвҖҷ -f ~/.ssh/id_dsa з”ҹжҲҗеҜҶеҢҷ&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;3-hadoopй…ҚзҪ®&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#3-hadoopй…ҚзҪ®&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;3.hadoopй…ҚзҪ®&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;3.hadoopй…ҚзҪ®&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;жҠҠдёӢиҪҪеҘҪзҡ„hadoopи§ЈеҺӢеҮәжқҘгҖӮпјҲжҲ‘зҡ„ең°еқҖеңЁ/rooзӣ®еҪ•,еҚіе®Ңж•ҙең°еқҖ/root/hadoopпјү   й…ҚзҪ®зҺҜеўғеҸҳйҮҸ vi ~/.bash_profile export HADOOP_HOME=/root/hadoop export PATH=$JAVA_HOME/bin:$PATH:$HOME/bin:$HADOOP_HOME/bin жү§иЎҢ . ~/.bash_profile дҪҝеҸҳйҮҸз”ҹж•Ҳ  &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;4-hadoopж–Үд»¶й…ҚзҪ®&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#4-hadoopж–Үд»¶й…ҚзҪ®&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;4.hadoopж–Үд»¶й…ҚзҪ®&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;4.hadoopж–Үд»¶й…ҚзҪ®&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;йҰ–е…Ҳз»ҷжң¬жңәе‘ҪеҗҚдёӘеҗҚеӯ—пјҡдҫӢеҰӮжҲ‘иҝҷиҫ№жҳҜs204   е°ұжү§иЎҢ hostnamectl set-hostname s204 еҸҳжӣҙдё»жңәеҗҚеӯ—   з„¶еҗҺеңЁ/root/hadoopзӣ®еҪ•дёӢ дҫқж¬Ўжү§иЎҢзј–иҫ‘&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;vim-etc-hadoop-core-site-xml&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#vim-etc-hadoop-core-site-xml&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;vim etc/hadoop/core-site.xml&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;vim etc/hadoop/core-site.xml&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;  еңЁ&lt;configuration&gt;&lt;/configuration&gt;дёӯеҠ е…Ҙ &lt;property&gt; &lt;name&gt;fs.defaultFS&lt;/name&gt; &lt;value&gt;hdfs://s204:9000&lt;/value&gt; &lt;/property&gt; &lt;property&gt; &lt;name&gt;hadoop.tmp.dir&lt;/name&gt; &lt;value&gt;file:/root/hadoop/tmp&lt;/value&gt; &lt;/property&gt; &lt;property&gt; &lt;name&gt;io.file.buffer.size&lt;/name&gt; &lt;value&gt;131702&lt;/value&gt; &lt;/property&gt; &lt;property&gt; &lt;name&gt;hadoop.proxyuser.hadoop.hosts&lt;/name&gt; &lt;value&gt;*&lt;/value&gt; &lt;/property&gt;   &lt;property&gt; &lt;name&gt;hadoop.proxyuser.hadoop.groups&lt;/name&gt; &lt;value&gt;*&lt;/value&gt; &lt;/property&gt;  &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;vim-etc-hadoop-hdfs-site-xml&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#vim-etc-hadoop-hdfs-site-xml&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;vim etc/hadoop/hdfs-site.xml&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;vim etc/hadoop/hdfs-site.xml&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;еңЁ&lt;configuration&gt;&lt;/configuration&gt;дёӯеҠ е…Ҙ   &lt;property&gt; &lt;name&gt;dfs.namenode.name.dir&lt;/name&gt; &lt;value&gt;file:/root/hadoop/hdfs/name&lt;/value&gt; &lt;/property&gt; &lt;property&gt; &lt;name&gt;dfs.datanode.data.dir&lt;/name&gt; &lt;value&gt;file:/root/hadoop/hdfs/data&lt;/value&gt; &lt;/property&gt; &lt;property&gt; &lt;name&gt;dfs.replication&lt;/name&gt; &lt;value&gt;3&lt;/value&gt; &lt;/property&gt; &lt;property&gt; &lt;name&gt;dfs.namenode.secondary.http-address&lt;/name&gt; &lt;value&gt;s204:9001&lt;/value&gt; &lt;/property&gt; &lt;property&gt; &lt;name&gt;dfs.webhdfs.enabled&lt;/name&gt; &lt;value&gt;true&lt;/value&gt; &lt;/property&gt;  &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;vim-etc-hadoop-mapred-site-xml&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#vim-etc-hadoop-mapred-site-xml&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;vim etc/hadoop/mapred-site.xml&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;vim etc/hadoop/mapred-site.xml&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;еңЁ&lt;configuration&gt;&lt;/configuration&gt;дёӯеҠ е…Ҙ   &lt;property&gt; &lt;name&gt;mapreduce.framework.name&lt;/name&gt; &lt;value&gt;yarn&lt;/value&gt; &lt;/property&gt; &lt;property&gt; &lt;name&gt;mapreduce.jobhistory.address&lt;/name&gt; &lt;value&gt;s204:10020&lt;/value&gt; &lt;/property&gt; &lt;property&gt; &lt;name&gt;mapreduce.jobhistory.webapp.address&lt;/name&gt; &lt;value&gt;s204:19888&lt;/value&gt; &lt;/property&gt;  &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;vim-etc-hadoop-yarn-site-xml&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#vim-etc-hadoop-yarn-site-xml&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;vim etc/hadoop/yarn-site.xml&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;vim etc/hadoop/yarn-site.xml&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;еңЁ&lt;configuration&gt;&lt;/configuration&gt;дёӯеҠ е…Ҙ &lt;property&gt; &lt;name&gt;yarn.nodemanager.aux-services&lt;/name&gt; &lt;value&gt;mapreduce_shuffle&lt;/value&gt; &lt;/property&gt; &lt;property&gt; &lt;name&gt;yarn.nodemanager.auxservices.mapreduce.shuffle.class&lt;/name&gt; &lt;value&gt;org.apache.hadoop.mapred.ShuffleHandler&lt;/value&gt; &lt;/property&gt; &lt;property&gt; &lt;name&gt;yarn.resourcemanager.address&lt;/name&gt; &lt;value&gt;s204:8032&lt;/value&gt; &lt;/property&gt; &lt;property&gt; &lt;name&gt;yarn.resourcemanager.scheduler.address&lt;/name&gt; &lt;value&gt;s204:8030&lt;/value&gt; &lt;/property&gt; &lt;property&gt; &lt;name&gt;yarn.resourcemanager.resource-tracker.address&lt;/name&gt; &lt;value&gt;s204:8031&lt;/value&gt; &lt;/property&gt; &lt;property&gt; &lt;name&gt;yarn.resourcemanager.admin.address&lt;/name&gt; &lt;value&gt;s204:8033&lt;/value&gt; &lt;/property&gt; &lt;property&gt; &lt;name&gt;yarn.resourcemanager.webapp.address&lt;/name&gt; &lt;value&gt;s204:8088&lt;/value&gt; &lt;/property&gt; &lt;property&gt; &lt;name&gt;yarn.nodemanager.resource.memory-mb&lt;/name&gt; &lt;value&gt;6078&lt;/value&gt; &lt;/property&gt;  &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;vim-etc-hadoop-yarn-env-sh&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#vim-etc-hadoop-yarn-env-sh&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;vim etc/hadoop/yarn-env.sh&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;vim etc/hadoop/yarn-env.sh&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;  дёӯжүҫеҲ° export JAVA_HOME еҺ»жҺүжіЁйҮҠ зј–иҫ‘javaең°еқҖ export JAVA_HOME=/usr/java/jdk1.8.0_121   жүҫеҲ°JAVA_HEAP_MAX=-Xmx1000m ж”№дёә JAVA_HEAP_MAX=-Xmx1024m  &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;vim-etc-hadoop-slaves&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#vim-etc-hadoop-slaves&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;vim etc/hadoop/slaves&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;vim etc/hadoop/slaves&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;  жё…з©әж·»еҠ  s204    &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;зҪ‘з»ңй…ҚзҪ®&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#зҪ‘з»ңй…ҚзҪ®&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;зҪ‘з»ңй…ҚзҪ®&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;зҪ‘з»ңй…ҚзҪ®&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;жҲ‘иҝҷipжҳҜ 192.168.5.9   зј–иҫ‘зҪ‘з»ңеӣәе®ҡip vim /etc/sysconfig/network-scripts/ifcfg-ens33   жҢҮе®ҡеӣәе®ҡip   TYPE=вҖқEthernetвҖқ #BOOTPROTO=вҖқdhcpвҖқ DEFROUTE=вҖқyesвҖқ PEERDNS=вҖқyesвҖқ PEERROUTES=вҖқyesвҖқ IPV4_FAILURE_FATAL=вҖқnoвҖқ IPV6INIT=вҖқyesвҖқ IPV6_AUTOCONF=вҖқyesвҖқ IPV6_DEFROUTE=вҖқyesвҖқ IPV6_PEERDNS=вҖқyesвҖқ IPV6_PEERROUTES=вҖқyesвҖқ IPV6_FAILURE_FATAL=вҖқnoвҖқ IPV6_ADDR_GEN_MODE=вҖқstable-privacyвҖқ NAME=вҖқens33вҖқ UUID=вҖқb9fe1e5c-be20-47f1-a2d3-e12f5ddb6aa1вҖқ DEVICE=вҖқens33вҖқ ONBOOT=вҖқyesвҖқ IPADDR0=192.168.5.9 PREFIX0=24 GATEWAY0=192.168.5.2 DNS1=114.114.114.114   з„¶еҗҺйҮҚеҗҜзҪ‘з»ң systemctl  restart  network   жү§иЎҢ ip add  жҹҘзңӢзҪ‘з»ңipжҳҜеҗҰе’Ңи®ҫе®ҡзҡ„дёҖиҮҙ  &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;HadoppеҗҜеҠЁ&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#HadoppеҗҜеҠЁ&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;HadoppеҗҜеҠЁ&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;HadoppеҗҜеҠЁ&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;  иҝӣе…Ҙ/root/hadoopзӣ®еҪ•   жү§иЎҢзј–иҜ‘ ./bin/hdfs namenode вҖ“format   з»“жһңеҖ’ж•°з¬¬дә”иЎҢеҮәзҺ° Exiting with status 0 еҲҷдёәжҲҗеҠҹ   з„¶еҗҺеҗҜеҠЁ ./sbin/start-all.sh   еҗҜеҠЁе®ҢжҜ•жү§иЎҢ./bin/hdfs dfsadmin вҖ“report жҹҘзңӢжҳҜеҗҰжңүиҠӮзӮ№ еҰӮжһңиҝ”еӣһ ж— жі•иҝһжҺҘеҲҷдёәеҗҜеҠЁеӨұиҙҘ   жү§иЎҢsystemctl stop firewalld.serviceе…ій—ӯйҳІзҒ«еўҷ  еңЁжөҸи§ҲеҷЁиҫ“е…Ҙs204:8088еҲҷеҸҜд»ҘзңӢеҲ°hadoopз•Ңйқў  &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&#34;е…¶д»–иҠӮзӮ№й…ҚзҪ®&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#е…¶д»–иҠӮзӮ№й…ҚзҪ®&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;е…¶д»–иҠӮзӮ№й…ҚзҪ®&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;е…¶д»–иҠӮзӮ№й…ҚзҪ®&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;д»ҘдёҠй…ҚзҪ®е®ҢжҜ•еҗҺпјҢе…ій—ӯcentos7 з„¶еҗҺе®Ңе…Ёе…ӢйҡҶпјҢеңЁж–°е…ӢйҡҶзҡ„зі»з»ҹдёӯпјҢжӣҙж”№ipең°еқҖе’Ңдё»жңәеҗҚ е…¶дёӯhadoopй…ҚзҪ®ж–Үд»¶ etc/hadoop/hdfs-site.xml  дёӯ &lt;property&gt; &lt;name&gt;dfs.datanode.data.dir&lt;/name&gt; &lt;value&gt;file:/root/hadoop/hdfs/data&lt;/value&gt; &lt;/property&gt;   зҡ„fileең°еқҖдёҚиғҪдёҖж ·гҖӮ жҲ‘иҝҷиҫ№дёүдёӘең°еқҖеҲҶеҲ«дёә file:/root/hadoop/hdfs/data file:/root/hadoop/hdfs/data/205 file:/root/hadoop/hdfs/data/206   е…ӢйҡҶе®ҢжҜ•пјҢй…ҚзҪ®ж–Үд»¶е’ҢipгҖҒдё»жңәеҗҚдҝ®ж”№еҘҪеҗҺгҖӮеңЁs204жңәеҷЁдёӯзј–иҫ‘ vim etc/hadoop/slaves еҠ е…Ҙ s205 s206   еӨҚеҲ¶sshд»ӨзүҢе…ҚеҜҶзҷ»еҪ• дҫӢеҰӮеӨҚеҲ¶еҲ°s205 scp &lt;del&gt;/.ssh/authorized_keys root@s205:&lt;/del&gt;/.ssh/   е…¶д»–еҸҰдёӘжңәеҷЁд№ҹдёҖж ·ж“ҚдҪң   еҸҰеӨ–еҮ дёӘжңәеҷЁд№ҹиҰҒзј–иҜ‘дёҖдёӢ   з„¶еҗҺеңЁs204еҒңжӯўhadoop   ./sbin/stop-all.sh   еҶҚж¬ЎеҗҜеҠЁ./sbin/start-all.sh   еңЁжөҸи§ҲеҷЁе°ұеҸҜд»ҘзңӢеҲ°дёүдёӘиҠӮзӮ№гҖӮ&lt;/p&gt;
